{"tid":1517552,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【經濟客飯】但求屈機之緊急法 - 曾國平","createTime":"2019-08-30T03:05:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T03:05:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e5ecd7607f41a7b3ad55d6973325e36a24658af6","tid":1517552,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:05:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20190830/20758859\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190830%2F20758859&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8mZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=1ccde909\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190830%2F20758859&h=83f6657f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20190830/20758859</a><br />\n<br />\n【經濟客飯】但求屈機之緊急法 - 曾國平<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190830/large/1567097616_2241.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190830%2Flarge%2F1567097616_2241.jpg&h=153d716f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警察越暴力，示威者越奮勇，一味靠嚇靠惡，只會提醒全世界特區政府是多麼的無能。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講過好多次，平息反修例衝突的主導權從來在特區政府。一再漠視市民訴求錯失降溫良機，甚至越治越亂，特首及其「班子」難辭其咎。最近行政會議成員湯家驊提出絕世好橋，政府可引用《緊急情況規例條例》進行立法。特首出席行政會議前，被問及會否引用條例時未有否認，指政府有責任檢視所有止暴制亂的法治手段。<br />\n<br />\n法例給予特首及行政會議極大權力：「法例在行政長官會同行政會議認為屬緊急情況或危害公安的情況時，行政長官會同行政會議可訂立任何他認為合乎公眾利益的規例」，包括「對刊物、文字、地圖、圖則、照片、通訊及通訊方法的檢查、管制及壓制」、「逮捕、羈留、驅逐及遞解離境」、「對財產及其使用作出的撥配、管制、沒收及處置」等等。再講得白一點，情況就如打機輸入cheat code屈機，讓政府權力升到999。<br />\n<br />\n打機入cheat code，過程變得沒有樂趣。特區政府入cheat code，香港又會有甚麼後果呢？商務及經濟發展局局長邱騰華，非常政治正確，指「看不到引用緊急法會對本港經濟有何影響」。這當然是假話。警察越暴力，示威者越奮勇，一味靠嚇靠惡，相信只會提醒全世界特區政府是多麼的無能，再次打擊投資者對香港的信心。<br />\n<br />\n曾國平<br />\n美國維珍尼亞理工大學經濟系副教授<br />\n<a href=\"http://fb.com/economics3.0/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Feconomics3.0%2F&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8mZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=94eb4c4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/economics3.0/</a><br />\n本欄逢周五刊出<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n【異動空間】業績期後點揀股 (魏力)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n【會師中環】港鐵只為大股東而生 (神仙丁)"},{"pid":"c1d31fc87f30268ff3ce749eb963d69179a7b931","tid":1517552,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:05:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mhik2fq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMhik2fq.gif&h=7b54c7c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8mZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=57118ebf\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8mZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=3e11db13\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8mZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=c91136d6\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"42c6f62b1e7bbcd70cda199c808c432f82eb269b","tid":1517552,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:05:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mhik2fq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMhik2fq.gif&h=7b54c7c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8mZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=5711